OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOutbreaks of patchy rain will
OL,6,Fsink south across the West Midlands
OL,7,Fduring Monday morning. This clearing
OL,8,Fto sunny spells into the afternoon.
OL,9,FFeeling rather chilly for the time of
OL,10,Fyear despite the sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry overnight with variable
OL,13,Famounts of cloud and lengthy clear
OL,14,Fspells developing. Chilly with a risk
OL,15,Fof a rural frost in the east. Turning
OL,16,Fcloudier across the northwest towards
OL,17,Fdawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
